snippet.textDisplay:
Beautiful. We don’t pay attention to stories from our historical past and in doing so lose a part or ourselves, what made us who we are today. I hope CS will keep telling those stories. This is just as much of an education for Pakistan as a nation as it is for the world.  Imagine how many minds have become curious now through this song, how many will get inspired to do things they never would’ve imagined. 
What a wonderful personality Shazia Manzoor has 🌸 
All credit goes to Xulfi for having the vision to bring together two artists who are seemingly worlds apart but so so good together.

snippet.textDisplay:
Coke Studio isn't just creating music, it's forging its own unique genres within Pakistani music.
I'm pleased that Xulfi stated, “This is just the beginning, we have much to explore and demonstrate to the world the potential of our music history.”
Imagine if we hadn't been colonized! That's it... It's time for us to shed this colonized mindset as a nation. Envision incorporating Mughal and traditional art back into our architecture?
The conceptualization of CS15 is truly commendable. Kudos to Xulfi and the team, especially those involved in the Creative Arts. 😍
